&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Users&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Names, emails, phones, DOB, company, job title&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Addresses&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Street, city, state, ZIP, coordinates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Transactions&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Amounts, merchants, categories, status&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


üè• Healthcare / HIPAA-Safe
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Patients&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî MRN, blood type, allergies, conditions, insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Medical Records&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî ICD-10 codes, vitals, visit types, clinical notes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Prescriptions&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Real medications, dosages, DEA numbers, NDC codes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Lab Results&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî 26 real lab tests with reference ranges and flags&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Insurance Claims&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî Charged/allowed/paid amounts, claim status&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Healthcare Providers&lt;/strong&gt; ‚Äî NPI numbers, specialties, credentials&lt;/li&gt;
