&lt;p&gt;üîë &lt;strong&gt;Key&lt;/strong&gt;: The domain defines &lt;strong&gt;WHAT&lt;/strong&gt; it needs, not &lt;strong&gt;HOW&lt;/strong&gt; it's implemented. This is &lt;strong&gt;dependency inversion&lt;/strong&gt; in action.&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;h2&gt;


üü¢ Layer 2: Application (Use Cases)
