&lt;h4&gt;


üí° Important observations:
&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Dependency injection&lt;/strong&gt;: Repository is injected through the constructor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Using clones&lt;/strong&gt;: We never directly mutate the entity obtained from the repository&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Existence validations&lt;/strong&gt;: We throw exceptions if the todo doesn't exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Thin layer&lt;/strong&gt;: Only orchestrates, doesn't contain complex business logic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;




&lt;h2&gt;


üü° Layer 3: Infrastructure (Technical Details)
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This layer contains &lt;strong&gt;concrete implementations&lt;/strong&gt; of ports and all integration with the outside world.&lt;/p&gt;

